description:
NOTE: This app does not provide support for HP TouchPad or WebOS products. Please use the on-device Help application to get assistance for issues related to your HP TouchPad or WebOS products. 

Get instant support for your HP Enterprise and Commercial Printers, Commercial laptops, commercial desktops, workstations and servers. Quickly resolve your issue or find answers using:
	•	24x7 chat Support with HP Support Specialists (Service in English available Worldwide on supported Products)
	•	Enhanced phone support via priority IVR Routing for North American customers.
	•	View recommended solutions and technical manuals specific to your product 
	•	Check warranty and active contract status for your commercial products.
